title: New Creator: Bret Kinsella
body:
Name: Bret Kinsella

Socials:
https://twitter.com/bretkinsella
https://voicebot.ai

Info:
Bret is founder, CEO, and editor of Voicebot.ai, the leading publication and research center for voice and AI technology. He was named voice AI analyst of the year and journalist of the year by Project Voice in 2020 and is widely cited in media and academic research as an authority on voice assistants and AI. He is also the host of the Voicebot Podcast and editor of the Voice Insider newsletter.

Use Cases:
Bot Coin will be used by a global community of bot creators to reward users and create fans while facilitating human-to-bot and bot-to-bot interactions. Independent chatbot and voice app developers in gaming, entertainment, and productivity will use the coins to reward fans and users, offer new features in exchange for coins, and compensate open source development contributors and other partners. Voicebot will also facilitate coin usage and loyalty programs through its own data and information-based products and services.  Together, these initiatives  will serve as a foundation for a community of AI-bot creators to jointly support the growth on the entire industry's user base and transaction volume. 

Community Treasury Grant Tier: $1,000

A 'yes' will approve Bret with a $1,000 Community Treasury Gift Coin grant.

A 'no' will deny this proposal.
